	<item>
		<title>The Web Is So Cool</title>
		<pubDate>Sat, 05 Jul 2025 12:05:00 +0900</pubDate>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">A98FB476-9A95-427A-8215-DBA24FCEF102</guid>
		<link>https://lmnt.me/blog/the-web-is-so-cool.html</link>
		<dc:creator>Louie Mantia</dc:creator>
		<description><![CDATA[
			<p>The web is so cool. Think about it. You can publish whatever, whenever. And when you do, it is instantly accessible around the globe.</p>
			<p>It’s one of the freest things. Present <strong>anything</strong> in <strong>any way you want</strong>, formatted <strong>exactly</strong> how you want. The only real limitation is the time it takes to do it. But in my experience, it’s absolutely always worth it.</p>
