					<td class="pink">P</td>
				</tr>
			</table>
			<p>Though these exact sequences do occur, surprisingly, there are <strong>other</strong> sequences that show up just as often. Let’s see how many times an exact color sequence was used.</p>
			<table>
				<tr>
					<th>M</th>
