		<description><![CDATA[
			<p>Luka is a very special person to me. We’ve known each other for <strong>ten years</strong> now. And I believe I’m a better designer and artist since having met them.</p>
			<p>For the past few weeks, Luka and I have been combing through every piece of art they’ve made, from <a href="https://grafera.zone/archive/illustrations/japan-bag-snacks-karin-koron.html">illustrations of snacks</a>, to <a href="https://grafera.zone/archive/digital/columbia-river-gorge-spring.html">digital landscapes</a>, to <a href="https://grafera.zone/archive/oil/zoetrope-raccoon.html">oil-painted zoetropes</a>.</p>
			<p>I’m proud to share a pretty big update to Luka’s website, <a href="https://grafera.zone"><strong>GraferaZone</strong></a>, which I built by forking <strong>LMNT</strong>, to display Luka’s art in the best light possible.</p>
