			<p><a href="https://lmnt.me/blog/icons/maihama-station.html">Download icons from LMNT</a></p>
			<hr>
			<p>Most <strong>JR East</strong> stations have circular or rectangular clocks, but at <strong>Maihama Station</strong> <small>(which services the Tokyo Disney Resort)</small>, they’re shaped like playing card suits!</p>
			<p>In addition, both platforms have Disney-themed chimes, which make fun <a href="https://lmnt.me/archive/ringtones/maihama-station/">ringtones</a>.</p>
			<h3>Adding iPhone Ringtones</h3>
			<ol>
				<li>Connect your iPhone to your computer with USB.</li>
				<li>Open <strong>Apple Music</strong> on your Mac.</li>
				<li>Select your device on the left.</li>
				<li>Drag the <strong>M4R</strong> ringtone files to your iPhone.</li>
				<li>On your iPhone, select your new ringtone!</li>
			</ol>
			<hr>
			<p>If you like this, you can <a class="button donate" href="https://donate.stripe.com/eVag0g952cl90aQ9AA">make a one-time donation</a>, <a href="https://patreon.com/LouieMantia">donate monthly</a>, or buy something from my <a class="button" href="https://lmnt.me/shop/">shop</a>.</p>
		]]></description>
